172 static int get_exts(void) {

174  if(max_loaded_major < 3) {
175 #endif
176  exts = (const char *)glGetString(GL_EXTENSIONS);
177 #ifdef _GLAD_IS_SOME_NEW_VERSION
178  } else {
179  unsigned int index;
180 
181  num_exts_i = 0;
182  glGetIntegerv(GL_NUM_EXTENSIONS, &num_exts_i);
183  if (num_exts_i > 0) {
184  exts_i = (char **)malloc((size_t)num_exts_i * (sizeof *exts_i));
185  }
186 
187  if (exts_i == NULL) {
188  return 0;
189  }
190 
191  for(index = 0; index < (unsigned)num_exts_i; index++) {
192  const char *gl_str_tmp = (const char*)glGetStringi(GL_EXTENSIONS, index);
193  size_t len = strlen(gl_str_tmp);
194 
195  char *local_str = (char*)malloc((len+1) * sizeof(char));
196  if(local_str != NULL) {
197  memcpy(local_str, gl_str_tmp, (len+1) * sizeof(char));
198  }
199  exts_i[index] = local_str;
200  }
201  }
202 #endif
203  return 1;
204 }

217 static int has_ext(const char *ext) {
218 #ifdef _GLAD_IS_SOME_NEW_VERSION
219  if(max_loaded_major < 3) {
220 #endif
221  const char *extensions;
222  const char *loc;
223  const char *terminator;
224  extensions = exts;
225  if(extensions == NULL || ext == NULL) {
226  return 0;
227  }
228 
229  while(1) {
230  loc = strstr(extensions, ext);
231  if(loc == NULL) {
232  return 0;
233  }
234 
235  terminator = loc + strlen(ext);
236  if((loc == extensions || *(loc - 1) == ' ') &&
237  (*terminator == ' ' || *terminator == '\0')) {
238  return 1;
239  }
240  extensions = terminator;
241  }
242 #ifdef _GLAD_IS_SOME_NEW_VERSION
243  } else {
244  int index;
245  if(exts_i == NULL) return 0;
246  for(index = 0; index < num_exts_i; index++) {
247  const char *e = exts_i[index];
248 
249  if(exts_i[index] != NULL && strcmp(e, ext) == 0) {
250  return 1;
251  }
252  }
253  }
254 #endif
255 
256  return 0;
257 }

1736 static int find_extensionsGL(void) {
1737  if (!get_exts()) return 0;
1738  (void)&has_ext;
1739  free_exts();
1740  return 1;
1741 }
1742 
1743 static void find_coreGL(void) {
1744 
1745  /* Thank you @elmindreda
1746  * https://github.com/elmindreda/greg/blob/master/templates/greg.c.in#L176
1747  * https://github.com/glfw/glfw/blob/master/src/context.c#L36
1748  */
1749  int i, major, minor;
1750 
1751  const char* version;
1752  const char* prefixes[] = {
1753  "OpenGL ES-CM ",
1754  "OpenGL ES-CL ",
1755  "OpenGL ES ",
1756  NULL
1757  };
1758 
1759  version = (const char*) glGetString(GL_VERSION);
1760  if (!version) return;
1761 
1762  for (i = 0; prefixes[i]; i++) {
1763  const size_t length = strlen(prefixes[i]);
1764  if (strncmp(version, prefixes[i], length) == 0) {
1765  version += length;
1766  break;
1767  }
1768  }
1769 
1770 /* PR #18 */
1771 #ifdef _MSC_VER
1772  sscanf_s(version, "%d.%d", &major, &minor);
1773 #else
1774  sscanf(version, "%d.%d", &major, &minor);
1775 #endif
1776 
1777  GLVersion.major = major; GLVersion.minor = minor;
1778  max_loaded_major = major; max_loaded_minor = minor;
1779  GLAD_GL_VERSION_1_0 = (major == 1 && minor >= 0) || major > 1;
1780  GLAD_GL_VERSION_1_1 = (major == 1 && minor >= 1) || major > 1;
1781  GLAD_GL_VERSION_1_2 = (major == 1 && minor >= 2) || major > 1;
1782  GLAD_GL_VERSION_1_3 = (major == 1 && minor >= 3) || major > 1;
1783  GLAD_GL_VERSION_1_4 = (major == 1 && minor >= 4) || major > 1;
1784  GLAD_GL_VERSION_1_5 = (major == 1 && minor >= 5) || major > 1;
1785  GLAD_GL_VERSION_2_0 = (major == 2 && minor >= 0) || major > 2;
1786  GLAD_GL_VERSION_2_1 = (major == 2 && minor >= 1) || major > 2;
1787  GLAD_GL_VERSION_3_0 = (major == 3 && minor >= 0) || major > 3;
1788  GLAD_GL_VERSION_3_1 = (major == 3 && minor >= 1) || major > 3;
1789  GLAD_GL_VERSION_3_2 = (major == 3 && minor >= 2) || major > 3;
1790  GLAD_GL_VERSION_3_3 = (major == 3 && minor >= 3) || major > 3;
1791  GLAD_GL_VERSION_4_0 = (major == 4 && minor >= 0) || major > 4;
1792  GLAD_GL_VERSION_4_1 = (major == 4 && minor >= 1) || major > 4;
1793  GLAD_GL_VERSION_4_2 = (major == 4 && minor >= 2) || major > 4;
1794  GLAD_GL_VERSION_4_3 = (major == 4 && minor >= 3) || major > 4;
1795  GLAD_GL_VERSION_4_4 = (major == 4 && minor >= 4) || major > 4;
1796  GLAD_GL_VERSION_4_5 = (major == 4 && minor >= 5) || major > 4;
1797  GLAD_GL_VERSION_4_6 = (major == 4 && minor >= 6) || major > 4;
1798  if (GLVersion.major > 4 || (GLVersion.major >= 4 && GLVersion.minor >= 6)) {
1799  max_loaded_major = 4;
1800  max_loaded_minor = 6;
1801  }
1802 }
1803 
1804 int gladLoadGLLoader(GLADloadproc load) {
1805  GLVersion.major = 0; GLVersion.minor = 0;
1806  glGetString = (PFNGLGETSTRINGPROC)load("glGetString");
1807  if(glGetString == NULL) return 0;
1808  if(glGetString(GL_VERSION) == NULL) return 0;
1809  find_coreGL();
1810  load_GL_VERSION_1_0(load);
1811  load_GL_VERSION_1_1(load);
1812  load_GL_VERSION_1_2(load);
1813  load_GL_VERSION_1_3(load);
1814  load_GL_VERSION_1_4(load);
1815  load_GL_VERSION_1_5(load);
1816  load_GL_VERSION_2_0(load);
1817  load_GL_VERSION_2_1(load);
1818  load_GL_VERSION_3_0(load);
1819  load_GL_VERSION_3_1(load);
1820  load_GL_VERSION_3_2(load);
1821  load_GL_VERSION_3_3(load);
1822  load_GL_VERSION_4_0(load);
1823  load_GL_VERSION_4_1(load);
1824  load_GL_VERSION_4_2(load);
1825  load_GL_VERSION_4_3(load);
1826  load_GL_VERSION_4_4(load);
1827  load_GL_VERSION_4_5(load);
1828  load_GL_VERSION_4_6(load);
1829 
1830  if (!find_extensionsGL()) return 0;
1831  return GLVersion.major != 0 || GLVersion.minor != 0;
1832 }
